{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After humans launched a nuclear war against each other, radiation caused the bugs and creatures on the earth to mutate, becoming abnormally large and ferocious, and gradually occupied most of the earth. Human territory was devoured, and leaders and armies of various countries evacuated to space on spaceships. The earth is no longer suitable for human habitation, and there are radiation and bugs everywhere...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Years later, you pick up your weapon, enter the abyss zone, and fight to the end against the swarm of insects! In the abyss, you can call for various supports such as drones, turrets, vehicles, mechs, etc. to fight against the swarm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Kill the swarm </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330400/extras/\u6d88\u706d\u866b\u7fa4.gif?t=1732205101\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Call the UAV</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330400/extras/\u53ec\u5524\u65e0\u4eba\u673a.gif?t=1732205101\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Call the turret</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330400/extras/\u53ec\u5524\u70ae\u5854.gif?t=1732205101\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Driving vehicle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330400/extras/\u9a7e\u9a76\u8f7d\u5177.gif?t=1732205101\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Driving mecha</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330400/extras/\u9a7e\u9a76\u673a\u7532.gif?t=1732205101\" /></p>","background":"https://shared